            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-24">
                    <p>A button gives thes user a way to triggter an immediate action. The colors used for the bakground and text of buttons have been vetted to meet a minimum color contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for accesibility purposes. Use the button classes on <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;button&gt;</code>, or <code>&lt;input&gt;</code> elements.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-24">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary">Primary</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-default">Secondary</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-link">Button link</a>

                    {{#markdown}}
```xml
<a class="btn [btn-primary] [btn-secondary] [btn-success] [btn-info] [btn-warning] [btn-danger] [disabled] [active]">
    Button link
</a>
```
                    {{/markdown}}
                </div>

                <div class="col-xs-24">
                    <h2>Buttons &amp; links on backgrounds</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4>Alt</h4>
                    <div class="color-black" style="padding: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-primary theme-alt">Primary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-secondary theme-alt">Secondary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-link theme-alt">Button link</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4>On solid color</h4>
                    <div class="color-fill-accent-vivid-high" style="padding: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-primary theme-on-color">Primary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-secondary theme-on-color">Secondary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-link theme-on-color">Button link</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4>On light image</h4>
                    <div class="example-light-image-bg" style="padding: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-primary theme-on-img-light">Primary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-secondary theme-on-img-light">Secondary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-link theme-on-img-light">Button link</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4>On dark image</h4>
                    <div class="example-dark-image-bg" style="padding: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em;">
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-primary theme-on-img-dark">Primary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-secondary theme-on-img-dark">Secondary</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-block btn-link theme-on-img-dark">Button link</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-xs-24">
                    {{#markdown}}
```xml
<a class="btn [btn-primary] [btn-secondary] [btn-link] [theme-alt] [theme-on-color] [theme-on-img-light] [theme-on-img-dark]">Button</a>
```
                    {{/markdown}}
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-xs-24">
                <h2>Toggle Button</h2>
                <button type="button" autocomplete="off" class="btn btn-secondary" data-toggle="button" aria-pressed="false">Toggle Button</button>
                <script>
                  window.addEventListener('onload', function()
                  {
                    $("[data-toggle='button']").button("toggle");
                  });
                </script>

                {{#markdown}}
```xml
<button type="button" autocomplete="off" class="btn btn-secondary" data-toggle="button" aria-pressed="false">Toggle Button</button>
<script>
  $("[data-toggle='button']").button("toggle");
</script>
```
                {{/markdown}}
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Toggle switch -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-24">
