                            <span class="stateLabel stateLabel-on">On</span>
                            <span class="stateLabel stateLabel-off">Off</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    {{#markdown}}
```xml
<button type="button" data-toggle="button" class="btn btn-toggle-switch" autocomplete="off" aria-pressed="false">
    <span class="stateLabel stateLabel-on">On</span>
    <span class="stateLabel stateLabel-off">Off</span>
</button>
```
                    {{/markdown}}
                </div>
